# Security Dashboard

[Back to App Admin](/app-admin)

## Recent Security Events (<%= @security_events.count %>)

<% if @security_events.any? -%>
| Time | Event Type | User | Details |
|------|------------|------|---------|
<% @security_events.each do |event| -%>
| <%= time_ago_in_words(event[:timestamp]) %> ago | <%= event[:event] || event["event"] %> | <%= event[:email] || event["email"] || '-' %> | <%= event[:reason] || event["reason"] || event[:admin_action] || event["admin_action"] || event[:request_path] || event["request_path"] || event[:details] || event["details"] %> |
<% end -%>
<% else -%>
*No recent security events.*
<% end -%>

## Suspended Users (<%= @suspended_users.count %>)

<% if @suspended_users.any? -%>
| User | Email | Suspended |
|------|-------|-----------|
<% @suspended_users.each do |user| -%>
| [<%= user.display_name || user.name %>](/app-admin/users/<%= user.id %>) | <%= user.email %> | <%= time_ago_in_words(user.suspended_at) %> ago |
<% end -%>
<% else -%>
*No suspended users.*
<% end -%>

## App Admins (<%= @app_admins.count %>)

<% if @app_admins.any? -%>
| User | Email |
|------|-------|
<% @app_admins.each do |user| -%>
| [<%= user.display_name || user.name %>](/app-admin/users/<%= user.id %>) | <%= user.email %> |
<% end -%>
<% else -%>
*No app admins configured.*
<% end -%>
